---
title: Sequence Diagram - Chatbot Create Booking
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Tamu
    participant UI as Halaman /chatbot
    participant API as /api/chat
    participant Auth as Supabase Auth
    participant LLM as Gemini 2.5
    participant Tool as Tool createBooking
    participant DB as Supabase

    Tamu->>UI: Klik "Book This Room"
    UI->>API: POST messages dengan tool call request
    API->>Auth: getUser() verifikasi sesi
    Auth-->>API: { user, email, fullName }
    alt User belum login
        API-->>UI: Login Prompt Card
        UI-->>Tamu: Tampilkan tombol Login
    else User sudah login
        API->>LLM: stream + verifiedUser context
        LLM->>Tool: createBooking({guestName, email, roomId, checkIn, checkOut, ...})
        Tool->>Tool: Generate booking_reference (BK######XXXX)
        Tool->>DB: INSERT INTO reservations (guest_id, room_id, check_in, check_out, status='confirmed', booking_reference)
        DB-->>Tool: { id, booking_reference }
        Tool-->>LLM: { success: true, bookingRef, totalAmount }
        LLM->>API: Stream konfirmasi
        API-->>UI: Tampilkan ringkasan reservasi
        UI-->>Tamu: Kode booking + instruksi pembayaran
    end
